short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Don't have enough ads interrupting your sight on the web? Just double them by clicking the icon!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you ever frustrated that the webpage you are on just doesn't have enough ads on it? This extension, with the click of a button, clones every ad on the site you are visiting.

Haven't done a book report and need an excuse to why? Just find a website you are using for research with ads on it and click away! 

Want to help out a web developer a little more? Just click it a few times and it'll help them earn a but more moolah!

The possibilities are endless with this extension, get started today!
